        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3679",
        "content": "When they opened the fish in order to cook it, everyone was astonished at finding such a little boy, and Tom was quite delighted at being free again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
