        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3679",
        "content": "Tom had traveled forty eight hours with a huge silver piece on his back, and was almost tired to death, when his mother ran out to meet him, and carried him into the house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
