        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3679",
        "content": "As Tom's clothes had suffered much in the batter pudding and the inside of the fish, his majesty ordered him a new suit of clothes and to be mounted as a knight on a mouse.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
