        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3679",
        "content": "The King was so charmed with his address that he ordered a little chair to be made, in order that Tom might sit upon his table, and also a palace of gold, a span high, with a door an inch wide, to live in.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
